Update text and link in all 22 language versions of the Release Notes packages. 
The 22 packages take the form: 
Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux-Release_Notes-6-as-XX-7-0.el6.noarch.rpm

Where XX is the two-letter langugage code. 

Each package should be updated to use the following content: 


For the official, up-to-date Red Hat Enterprise Linux 6.7 Release Notes, refer to:

https://access.redhat.com/site/documentation/en-US/Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux/6/html/6.7_Release_Notes/index.html
