Update text and link in all 22 language versions of the Release Notes packages. 
The 22 packages take the form: 
Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux-Release_Notes-6-$LANG-7-0.el6.noarch.rpm

where $LANG is a language code like en-US, ru-RU, ja-JP, etc.
Done for all non-Indic languages.
